        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>Insurance is often a concept that's put on the back burner by college students, overshadowed by more immediate concerns of academics and social life. However, understanding insurance is a crucial aspect of adult life and financial planning. This article will introduce you to the basics of insurance, its importance, and the types of insurance that are particularly relevant to students.</p>
